org.miniauth.oauth.common

Class OAuthIncomingRequestBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.miniauth.oauth.common.OAuthIncomingRequestBuilder

  • public final class OAuthIncomingRequestBuilder
extends Object
    Builds an OAuthIncomingRequest object. (a) Construct OAuthIncomingRequestBuilder or call init() on existing Builder. (b) Set attributes. (c) Call build() to create OAuthIncomingRequest.
